            <header class="article-header">
                <span class="article-category">Automatizaci√≥n</span>
                <h1 class="article-title">Por qu√© invertir en automatizaci√≥n es m√°s rentable que contratar m√°s personal</h1>
                <div class="article-meta">
                    <span><i class="fas fa-calendar"></i> 18 Agosto 2025</span>
